<plot>The film traces the schism in the Bulgarian church. Some of the reasons for it are rooted in the Bulgarian history, others - in the events of the last several years. The people's need for faith is in contradiction with the petty quarrels of the higher clergy, who have forgotten their mission of being spiritual leaders.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?287615</url></doc>
